---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';

const siteUrl = "https://jagsyjoy-website.pages.dev";
const canonicalUrl = `${siteUrl}/policy/shipping-policy`;
const ogImage = `${siteUrl}/images/blog-1.jpg`;
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Shipping Policy | Jagsy Joy</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Read the Jagsy Joy shipping policy, including processing, shipping times, tracking, and shipping support."
    />
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalUrl} />

    <!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Shipping Policy | Jagsy Joy" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Read the Jagsy Joy shipping policy, including processing, shipping times, tracking, and shipping support." />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />

    <!-- Twitter -->
    <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta property="twitter:url" content={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta property="twitter:title" content="Shipping Policy | Jagsy Joy" />
    <meta property="twitter:description" content="Read the Jagsy Joy shipping policy, including processing, shipping times, tracking, and shipping support." />
    <meta property="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </head>

  <body>
    <AnnouncementBar />
    <Header />

    <main>
      <header class="policy-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">POLICY</p>
        <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="container">
        <article class="policy-card">
          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">🚚</span>
              <h2>Shipping Policy</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Currently, we are running a limited-time offer for <strong>Free Shipping within the US</strong>.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">📦</span>
              <h2>Order Processing</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Orders are typically processed and prepared for shipment within 1-2 business days. You will receive a notification once your curious little explorer's toys are on their way.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">⏱️</span>
              <h2>Shipping Times</h2>
            </div>
            <p>We offer Expedited Shipping (3–5 days) and Standard Shipping (5–10 days) to the United States, Canada, and Mexico.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">🔍</span>
              <h2>Tracking</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive an email with a tracking number so you can follow your Jagsy Joy adventure right to your doorstep.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">⚠️</span>
              <h2>Shipping Issues</h2>
            </div>
            <p>If your package is delayed, lost, or arrives damaged, please contact us immediately so we can make it right for you and your little one.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <div class="section-title">
              <span class="icon-badge">✉️</span>
              <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            </div>
            <p>If you have any questions or inquiries, please email <strong>support@finessynyc.com</strong>. Our team will get back to you within 24 hours.</p>
          </section>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: #17204A;
    background: #EAFBFF;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.08), transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 90% 4%, rgba(24, 214, 201, 0.08), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #EAFBFF 0%, #F4FDFF 50%, #EEE8FF 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .policy-header {
    padding: 220px 8% 60px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: #17204A;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #17204A;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 8% 120px;
  }

  .policy-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #D1EFFF;
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 60px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.04);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .icon-badge {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #EAFBFF;
    border: 1px solid #D1EFFF;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #17204A;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #5f526b;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  strong {
    color: #17204A;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .policy-header {
      padding-top: 150px;
    }
    
    .policy-card {
      padding: 40px 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>